{"tid":2326931,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英首相下月訪印  料為建立抗中民主10國聯盟作準備","createTime":"2020-12-15T16:11:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T21:02:48.000Z","uid":305299,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"1aae52328ec8b64a1799aa5584fcc9f09b41bbb7","tid":2326931,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T16:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rf3M8wL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRf3M8wL.jpg&h=d272b505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國首相府今日 (15號) 公佈，將會下個月出訪印度，預期其中一個出訪討論嘅議題係，籌備建立抗衡中國嘅民主10國聯盟。<br />\n<br />\n前兩個禮拜，英國國會議員組成嘅中國研究小組發表長達 38 頁嘅對華政策報告，當中提出9大建議，包括制定英國版《香港自治法》、協助 BNO 將資產快速安全轉移到英國、以及聯合其他民主國家一齊組織稱為「D10聯盟」嘅同盟來抗衡中國。而 D10 聯盟預料會包括印度、澳洲、南韓同現有七大工業國組織 (G7) 成員，亦即係美國、加拿大、法國、德國、意大利、日本同英國本身。<br />\n<br />\n首相府嘅公佈入面亦都有提到，首相莊漢生已經寫咗信邀請印度、澳洲同南韓出席下年暑假，由英國作為東道主舉辦嘅 G7 峰會。<br />\n<br />\n另外，外相藍韜文已經喺禮拜一到達印度出訪四日，同時為下個月首相訪問印度嘅行程提前作出準備。<br />\n<br />\n= = = = = 傳送門 = = = = =<br />\n英國衛報報導<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/dec/15/boris-johnson-to-visit-india-in-january-in-bid-to-transform-g7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2020%2Fdec%2F15%2Fboris-johnson-to-visit-india-in-january-in-bid-to-transform-g7&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGJnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=a22d58f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/dec/15/boris-johnson-to-visit-india-in-january-in-bid-to-transform-g7</a><br />\n<br />\n英國首相府新聞稿<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/news/boris-johnson-to-visit-india-to-boost-jobs-and-prosperity\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fnews%2Fboris-johnson-to-visit-india-to-boost-jobs-and-prosperity&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGJnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=927dc85d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/government/news/boris-johnson-to-visit-india-to-boost-jobs-and-prosperity</a><br />\n<br />\n英國會中國研究小組：應協助BNO入稟國際法庭同快速安全轉移資產<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2307919\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2307919</a>"},{"pid":"8f16c4d3a910dd50f43308fad6076434957f0b4a","tid":2326931,"uid":106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T16:11:50.000Z","msg":"日出"},{"pid":"34ef14a316313f084e0b546f34986ef61cfd3290","tid":2326931,"uid":227271,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T16:12:16.000Z","msg":"正過返印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90fbe76641cf7e233365c6f3771d91b3a42791ef","tid":2326931,"uid":306340,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T16:14:36.000Z","msg":"連英印矛盾都可以化解<br />\n厲害了我的蟈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e738f857752983cf4f6a5b686693d06140e81536","tid":2326931,"uid":144626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T16:15:20.000Z","msg":"印巴以前都係英國殖民地<br />\n唔知點解成日覺得英國同印度親過巴基咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c485caca8329fdf337f53219d5fffed3325b28","tid":2326931,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T16:29:01.000Z","msg":"可惜美國已經日落"},{"pid":"5671b89864f9fa10d07c517c8a42995806b0c8b0","tid":2326931,"uid":258258,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T16:30:31.000Z","msg":"外相藍韜文已經喺禮拜一到達印度出訪四日<br />\n<br />\n解決左個外交部先啦，全部支那D人點傾呀，大鳴大放呀？"},{"pid":"24cc45486d566cea5114f55424243f02aa4274a9","tid":2326931,"uid":70487,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T16:31:42.000Z","msg":"多得阿Trump反共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.insider.com/5a8a52fad0307226028b463f?width=1200&amp;format=jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbna